    <li><strong>Live Cursors</strong>: See who's currently viewing or editing the list</li>
    <li><strong>Activity Feed</strong>: Track who added, edited, or completed items</li>
    <li><strong>Conflict Resolution</strong>: Automatic handling of simultaneous edits</li>
    <li><strong>Offline Changes</strong>: Sync changes when connection is restored</li>
  </ul>

